; Coverage for commodity.cc recursion found disparity in comparison
; Two lots of the same commodity with different price commodities and numeric values
; The comparison function recurses to compare numeric values, finds a disparity

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {200.00 EUR}
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
      10 AAPL {$150}
     5 AAPL {EUR200}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
